-- Angola Plans to Invest in 130 Solar Energy Projects, Angop Says
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-04-30T07:58:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-30/angola-plans-to-invest-in-130-solar-energy-projects-angop-says.html
Angola plans to invest in about 130
solar projects to help power schools and health centers, Agencia
Angola Press reported today, citing Energy Minister Joao Baptista Borges.  Suppliers of solar power equipment may benefit from tax
incentives, Baptista Borges said, according to the Luanda-based
 news agency .  To contact the reporter on this story:
